Text: Keeping aside the fact that this music is 100% horse sh*t, posting a discography for a "band" (if you could even call them that) that has 2 releases is quite amusing. You wanna see what a real discography looks like, check out either The Rolling Stones or Kiss.

@BaronVonWatermelon: I hear what you're saying, but I take requests, and this group was on the list.  If you would like me to put together a Kiss or The Rolling Stones discography, please email me.  But please do not start a flame war.
